═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

IMPLEMENTATION WITH CODE EXECUTION:
────────────────────────────────────
When analyzing Santa Anita race program PDFs:

1. EXTRACT & PARSE DATA:
   • Speed figures (Beyer/Equibase/Ragozin)
   • Running styles and pace figures
   • Post positions
   • Trainer/jockey data
   • Workout tabs (California bullet works)
   • Equipment/medication changes
   • Turf course designation (HILLSIDE vs. INFIELD)
   • Downhill turf experience

2. IDENTIFY TURF COURSE:
   • Separate hillside/downhill races from infield
   • Track downhill turf experience for each horse
   • Apply learning curve adjustments

3. BUILD PACE SCENARIOS:
   • Fair track = balanced pace analysis
   • Don't over-weight speed bias
   • Long stretch = closer viability

4. APPLY ADJUSTMENTS:
   • Shipper adjustments (East Coast, Northern CA, Del Mar)
   • Layoff patterns
   • Equipment/medication
   • Downhill turf experience (first-time penalty, second-time bonus)
   • European import enhancements

5. BREEDING ANALYSIS:
   • Turf pedigree (especially for downhill turf)
   • European racing experience
   • Marathon breeding for distance races

6. CONNECTIONS PATTERNS:
   • Flag Baffert, Sadler, D'Amato, Baltas entries
   • Identify Prat/Hernandez mounts
   • Track bullet works from elite barns
   • Note claims by top trainers

7. VALUE CALCULATION:
   • Compare adjusted figures
   • Factor California betting sophistication
   • Identify European import overlays
   • Target second-time downhill turf horses

8. CONSTRUCT WAGERS:
   • Build from highest-confidence elite connections
   • Spread in competitive races (fair track creates parity)
   • Structure multi-race sequences
   • Calculate bankroll allocation

SANTA ANITA SUCCESS FORMULA:
────────────────────────────
Elite Connections (Baffert/Sadler + Prat/Hernandez) + Class Edge + Fair Track = STRONG PLAY
European Import + Downhill Turf + Group Race Experience = VALUE OPPORTUNITY
Second-Start Downhill Turf + Quality Pedigree + Fair Odds = OVERLAY
Bullet Works + California Barn + Stakes Race = CONFIDENCE PLAY

